1. (0 marks) Learn the basics of html, css and php.

2. (30 marks) Create a database of students, courses and faculty members in
SQLite.  For every entity, you should have a table.  Think of the relevant
attributes for each table.  Link the student table to courses.  In particular,
ensure that the enrollment of a student in a course is captured.  If required,
use another table.  Make sure the declarations about data types, primary keys
and foreign keys are correctly made.  In the enrollment table, create
attributes for total marks and grade.  Write SQL statements to compute the
total and grade given the marks for assignments, quizzes, exams, etc.

Insert data by reading from a file.

Write several interesting query statements in SQL.  Output the results in a
file.

